														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1136585">
									

<p>Psi-8 is the MTF that &quot;find all forms of communication between graves and the surface, normally put into place as a precaution against accidental burial, such as pipes, bells, and even phones, and sever them&quot;.</p>
<p>I'd guess that if heads suddenly removed themselves from dead bodies and started to act like crabs, these guys would find out about it first. Their involvement probably means that the Foundation suspects that more instances of 565 can be created from dead bodies buried in cemeteries.</p>
<p>I like this one, although I can't help but think that it'd be creepier if acted more like a jellyfish instead of a crab. Imagining this thing moving by crawling near the ground makes it look kinda silly; if it was just a slowly floating head with a bunch of brain-tentacles dragging behind it&#8230; brr.</p>

							</div>

								
					
